			<div class="caption-text">The Gear 2's various bits and pieces.</div>
	
			<div class="caption-credit">
							<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/Samsung+Gear+2+Teardown/23990">iFixit</a>
				</div>
